data.description: Welcome to this charming 2 bed/2bath+bonus home nestled on a .42-acre lot in the heart of Jamestown. Boasting a prime central location & free from any restrictions, this property offers both convenience & freedom. With a comfortable 1,424 square feet of living space, this home is the perfect blend of affordability & spaciousness. Step inside to discover a warm & inviting living area featuring a gas log fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for those chilly TN evenings. The open-concept design flows seamlessly into the dining & kitchen areas, making it a great space for entertaining. The kitchen is equipped with plenty of counter space for your culinary endeavors. The master bedroom is a cozy retreat, complete with a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms offer versatility for guests, a home office, or a growing family. Whether you have green thumbs or simply want room for outdoor activities, your front & back yards have you covered. Come see this great home with no restrictions&no HOA!
